An '''Iron Bar''' is created by smelting 5 [[Iron Ore]] in a [[furnace]] with 1 [[coal]] for fuel, or by [[Crafting]] the "Transmute (Fe)" recipe (3 [[Copper Bar]]s into one Iron Bar which is unlocked at mining level 4).  

Iron Bars may occasionally be found in [[Garbage Can]]s after receiving the [[Furnace]] blueprints from [[Clint]].  An Iron Bar may also drop from a [[Shadow Brute]] (2% chance) or [[Shadow Shaman]] (2% chance) when slain.

Smelting iron ore in a furnace takes 2 in-game hours.  The "Transmute (Fe)" recipe is earned at [[Mining]] Level 4.

Iron bars are used in a variety of [[crafting]] recipes and are used to upgrade [[tools]] to tier 3. Each iron bar can be sold for {{price|120}}, or {{price|180}} with the [[Skills#Mining|Blacksmith Profession]].

==Tool Upgrades==
Iron Bars are required for the second upgrade of tools.

