==Bundles==
An Iron Bar is used in the {{Bundle|Blacksmith||y}}.

==Tailoring==
An Iron Bar is used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] to create the [[Tailoring|Steel Breastplate]].  [[File:Shirt148.png|24px]]

==Quests==
*[[Clint]] requests an Iron Bar by mail on the 17th of [[Winter]] in the [[Quests#A Favor For Clint|"A Favor for Clint" quest]].  The reward is {{Price|500}} and 1 [[Friendship]] heart.
*An Iron Bar may be randomly requested during any season at the [[Quests#Help Wanted Quests|"Help Wanted" Board]] outside [[Pierre's General Store]] for a reward of {{Price|360}} and 150 [[Friendship]] points.  An Iron Bar will never be requested until you have the [[Furnace]] blueprints.  
*Three or four Iron Bars may be requested by [[Catfish]], [[Ice Pip]], or [[Spook Fish]] in [[Fish Pond#Quests|Fish Pond quests]].

==Notes==
*When selling Iron Bars, crafting them into Gold Bars first increases the profit by {{price|10}} per Gold Bar ({{price|15}} with the Blacksmith profession).

==History==
{{History|1.4|Can now be used in [[Tailoring]]. Can be requested in [[Fish Pond#Quests|Fish Pond quests]].}}

